iv class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-rocket h-6 w-6 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 15v5s3.03-.55 4-2c1.08-1.62 0-5 0-5\"></path><path d=\"M4.5 16.5c-1.5 1.26-2 5-2 5s3.74-.5 5-2c.71-.84.7-2.13-.09-2.91a2.18 2.18 0 0 0-2.91-.09\"></path><path d=\"M9 12a22 22 0 0 1 2-3.95A12.88 12.88 0 0 1 22 2c0 2.72-.78 7.5-6 11a22.4 22.4 0 0 1-4 2z\"></path><path d=\"M9 12H4s.55-3.03 2-4c1.62-1.08 5 .05 5 .05\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold\">04</div></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2 pt-2\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-xl text-foreground\">Entrega y ajustes</h3><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Publicamos tu web y hacemos los ajustes finales.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"projects\" class=\"container mx-auto px-6 py-20 lg:py-28\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"css-0\" style=\"opacity:0;animation-delay:0ms\"><div class=\"text-center space-y-4 mb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Soluciones que impulsan negocios</h2><p class=\"text-lg md:text-xl text-muted-foreground\">Ejemplos de proyectos activos y arquitecturas diseñadas para resultados reales</p></div></div><div class=\"css-0\" style=\"opacity:0;animation-delay:200ms\"><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12\"><a class=\"group relative\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://online-catalog.auroralabs.com.ar/\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-primary/5 rounded-xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 blur-xl transition-opacity duration-300\"></div><div class=\"relative bg-background rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-border/50 hover:border-border transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg\"><div class=\"relative h-48 overflow-hidden bg-muted\"><img src=\"/projects/burger-punk.webp\" alt=\"Burger Punk\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500\"/><div class=\"absolute top-3 right-3\"><div class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-background/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full text-xs font-medium border border-border/50\">Catálogo</div></div></div><div class=\"p-6 space-y-3\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg text-foreground\">Burger Punk</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Concepto de catálogo digital autogestionable con pedidos por WhatsApp. Ideal para locales gastronómicos y showrooms.</p><div class=\"pt-3 border-t border-border/50\"><p class=\"text-sm font-medium text-primary\">Interfaz optimizada para móviles</p></div></div></div></a><a class=\"group relative\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://pagina-corporativa.auroralabs.com.ar/\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-primary/5 rounded-xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 blur-xl transition-opacity duration-300\"></div><div class=\"relative bg-background rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-border/50 hover:border-border transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg\"><div class=\"relative h-48 overflow-hidden bg-muted\"><img src=\"/projects/nexo-contadores.webp\" alt=\"Nexo Contadores\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500\"/><div class=\"absolute top-3 right-3\"><div class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-background/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full text-xs font-medium border border-border/50\">Empresa</div></div></div><div class=\"p-6 space-y-3\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg text-foreground\">Nexo Contadores</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Modelo de web corporativa multisección para estudios profesionales, enfocada en la autoridad y la confianza del cliente.</p><div class=\"pt-3 border-t border-border/50\"><p class=\"text-sm font-medium text-primary\">Estructura SEO Friendly y Blog CMS</p></div></div></div></a><a class=\"group relative\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://landing-page.auroralabs.com.ar/\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-primary/5 rounded-xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 blur-xl transition-opacity duration-300\"></div><div class=\"relative bg-background rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-border/50 hover:border-border transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg\"><div class=\"relative h-48 overflow-hidden bg-muted\"><img src=\"/projects/flare-initiative.webp\" alt=\"The Flare Initiative\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500\"/><div class=\"absolute top-3 right-3\"><div class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-background/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full text-xs font-medium border border-border/50\">Landing</div></div></div><div class=\"p-6 space-y-3\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg text-foreground\">The Flare Initiative</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Landing page de alto impacto para servicios profesionales, optimizada para la captura de leads y conversión directa.</p><div class=\"pt-3 border-t border-border/50\"><p class=\"text-sm font-medium text-primary\">Arquitectura nativa de carga instantánea</p></div></div></div></a></div></div><div class=\"css-0\" style=\"opacity:0;animation-delay:400ms\"><div class=\"text-center\"><a href=\"#contact\"><button data-slot=\"button\" data-variant=\"outline\" data-size=\"lg\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium transition-all disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg:not([class*=&#x27;size-&#x27;])]:size-4 shrink-0 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 outline-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 aria-invalid:border-destructive border bg-background shadow-xs hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground dark:bg-input/30 dark:border-input dark:hover:bg-input/50 h-10 rounded-md px-6 has-[&gt;svg]:px-4 group\">Consultar por mi proyecto<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right ml-2 h-4 w-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></button></a></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 lg:py-28 relative overflow-hidden bg-muted/30\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6 relative\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"css-0\" style=\"opacity:0;animation-delay:0ms\"><div class=\"text-center space-y-4 mb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground\">Preguntas frecuentes</h2><p class=\"text-lg md:text-xl text-muted-foreground\">Respuestas claras, sin vueltas ni tecnicismos innecesarios.</p></div></div><div class=\"css-0\" style=\"opacity:0;animation-delay:200ms\"><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"bg-background rounded-xl border border-border/50 overflow-hidden hover:border-border transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm\"><button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between p-5 md:p-6 text-left hover:bg-muted/50 transition-colors\"><span class=\"font-semibold text-lg text-foreground pr-4\">¿En cuánto tiempo tendré mi web lista?</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down h-5 w-5 text-primary flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button><div class=\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out max-h-0 opacity-0\"><div class=\"px-5 md:px-6 pb-5 md:pb-6 pt-0\"><div class=\"h-px bg-border/50 mb-4\"></div><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-base\">Landing Pages en 1 semana, Webs Institucionales en 2-3 y E-commerce en 4 semanas.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-background rounded-xl border border-border/50 overflow-hidden hover:border-border transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm\"><button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between p-5 md:p-6 text-left hover:bg-muted/50 transition-colors\"><span class=\"font-semibold text-lg text-foreground pr-4\">¿Mi web va a aparecer en los primeros resultados de Google?</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down h-5 w-5 text-primary flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button><div class=\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out max-h-0 opacity-0\"><div class=\"px-5 md:px-6 pb-5 md:pb-6 pt-0\"><div class=\"h-px bg-border/50 mb-4\"></div><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-base\">Te entrego una base técnica impecable para que Google te   quiera, pero el SEO es un camino largo.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-background rounded-xl border border-border/50 overflow-hidden hover:border-border transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm\"><button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between p-5 md:p-6 text-left hover:bg-muted/50 transition-colors\"><span class=\"font-semibold text-lg text-foreground pr-4\">¿Podré gestionar el contenido yo mismo?</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down h-5 w-5 text-primary flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button><div class=\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out max-h-0 opacity-0\"><div class=\"px-5 md:px-6 pb-5 md:pb-6 pt-0\"><div class=\"h-px bg-border/50 mb-4\"></div><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-base\">¡Obvio! Según el plan, tenés autonomía para manejar lo tuyo. Por ejemplo: en webs corporativas podés subir tus propios blogs; en catálogos, gestionás productos; y en E-commerce, tenés control total de clientes, ventas y productos. Vos te encargás del contenido y yo de que el código siga siendo puro y vuele.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-background rounded-xl border border-border/50 overflow-hidden hover:border-border transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm\"><button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between p-5 md:p-6 text-left hover:bg-muted/50 transition-colors\"><span class=\"font-semibold text-lg text-foreground pr-4\">¿Qué incluye el servicio de mantenimiento?</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down h-5 w-5 text-primary flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button><div class=\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out max-h-0 opacity-0\"><div class=\"px-5 md:px-6 pb-5 md:pb-6 pt-0\"><div class=\"h-px bg-border/50 mb-4\"></div><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-base\">Hosting, SSL, backups y soporte técnico. Es tener un departamento de sistemas a disposición.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-background rounded-xl border border-border/50 overflow-hidden hover:border-border transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm\"><button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between p-5 md:p-6 text-left hover:bg-muted/50 transition-colors\"><span class=\"font-semibold text-lg text-foreground pr-4\">¿Y si el diseño final no me gusta?</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down h-5 w-5 text-primary flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button><div class=\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out max-h-0 opacity-0\"><div class=\"px-5 md:px-6 pb-5 md:pb-6 pt-0\"><div class=\"h-px bg-border/50 mb-4\"></div><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-base\">Validamos todo antes de programar, así que no hay sorpresas desagradables.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-background rounded-xl border border-border/50 overflow-hidden hover:border-border transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm\"><button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between p-5 md:p-6 text-left hover:bg-muted/50 transition-colors\"><span class=\"font-semibold text-lg text-foreground pr-4\">¿Por qué elegir código personalizado?</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down h-5 w-5 text-primary flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button><div class=\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out max-h-0 opacity-0\"><div class=\"px-5 md:px-6 pb-5 md:pb-6 pt-0\"><div class=\"h-px bg-border/50 mb-4\"></div><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-base\">Porque es más rápido, seguro y no es una copia barata de una plantilla que usa todo el mundo.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-background rounded-xl border border-border/50 overflow-hidden hover:border-border transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm\"><button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between p-5 md:p-6 text-left hover:bg-muted/50 transition-colors\"><span class=\"font-semibold text-lg text-foreground pr-4\">¿Cuál es la diferencia entre un ajuste de contenido y un ajuste de diseño?</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down h-5 w-5 text-primary flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button><div class=\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out max-h-0 opacity-0\"><div class=\"px-5 md:px-6 pb-5 md:pb-6 pt-0\"><div class=\"h-px bg-border/50 mb-4\"></div><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-base\">Un ajuste de contenido es para cambios puntuales de información: actualizar un texto, cambiar el logo, o retocar un color específico sin alterar el resto. Un ajuste de diseño implica cambios más profundos, como modificar o eliminar una sección entera, cambiar animaciones o reestructurar cómo se navega la página.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"contact\" class=\"py-20 lg:py-28 relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-muted/30 via-muted/50 to-muted/30 pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-primary/5 to-purple-500/5 pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6 relative\"><div class=\"css-0\" style=\"opacity:0;animation-delay:0ms\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center space-y-8\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Convierte visitantes en clientes</h2><p class=\"text-lg md:text-xl text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Hablemos de tu proyecto. Sin compromiso ni letra chica.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center pt-4\"><a href=\"https://wa.me/5492926501348?text=Hola!%20Me%20gustar%C3%ADa%20recibir%20m%C3%A1s%20informaci%C3%B3n%20sobre%20sus%20servicios%20de%20desarrollo%20web.\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><button data-slot=\"button\" data-variant=\"default\" data-size=\"lg\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium transition-all disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg:not([class*=&#x27;size-&#x27;])]:size-4 shrink-0 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 outline-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 aria-invalid:border-destructive bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90 h-10 rounded-md px-6 has-[&gt;svg]:px-4 group\"><svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\" class=\"h-5 w-5 mr-2\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M380.9 97.1C339 55.1 283.2 32 223.9 32c-122.4 0-222 99.6-222 222 0 39.1 10.2 77.3 29.6 111L0 480l117.7-30.9c32.4 17.7 68.9 27 106.1 27h.1c122.3 0 224.1-99.6 224.1-222 0-59.3-25.2-115-67.1-157zm-157 341.6c-33.2 0-65.7-8.9-94-25.7l-6.7-4-69.8 18.3L72 359.2l-4.4-7c-18.5-29.4-28.2-63.3-28.2-98.2 0-101.7 82.8-184.5 184.6-184.5 49.3 0 95.6 19.2 130.4 54.1 34.8 34.9 56.2 81.2 56.1 130.5 0 101.8-84.9 184.6-186.6 184.6zm101.2-138.2c-5.5-2.8-32.8-16.2-37.9-18-5.1-1.9-8.8-2.8-12.5 2.8-3.7 5.6-14.3 18-17.6 21.8-3.2 3.7-6.5 4.2-12 1.4-32.6-16.3-54-29.1-75.5-66-5.7-9.8 5.7-9.1 16.3-30.3 1.8-3.7.9-6.9-.5-9.7-1.4-2.8-12.5-30.1-17.1-41.2-4.5-10.8-9.1-9.3-12.5-9.5-3.2-.2-6.9-.2-10.6-.2-3.7 0-9.7 1.4-14.8 6.9-5.1 5.6-19.4 19-19.4 46.3 0 27.3 19.9 53.7 22.6 57.4 2.8 3.7 39.1 59.7 94.8 83.8 35.2 15.2 49 16.5